## 7. CVaR Optimization

Runs the full CVaR optimizer with Ledoit-Wolf shrinkage and Longin-Solnik tail correlations. Uses the ETF auto-selector to pick best-in-class funds (e.g. FCOM over XLC, SGOV over BIL).

Includes a **current-holdings fallback** if the optimizer returns zero positions — the notebook will continue rather than dying silently.
